            "value" : "· %lld 核 GPU"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "“%@” will be removed from your library and its downloaded files deleted to free up disk space. This can't be undone, but you can download it again from the Workshop." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「%@」はライブラリから削除され、ダウンロード済みファイルは空き容量を増やすために削除されます。この操作は元に戻せませんが、Workshop から再度ダウンロードできます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“%@”将从你的库中移除，其已下载文件会被删除以释放磁盘空间。此操作无法撤销，但你可以再次从 Workshop 下载。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「%@」會從你的資料庫中移除，其已下載檔案會被刪除以釋放磁碟空間。此操作無法復原，但你可以再次從 Workshop 下載。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "“%@” will be removed from your library. Its original files (imported from your own folder) are left untouched." : {
      "comment" : "A confirmation dialog message for removing a wallpaper from the library. The argument is the name of the wallpaper.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「%@」はライブラリから削除されます。元のファイル（自分のフォルダから読み込んだもの）は変更されません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“%@”将从你的库中移除。其原始文件（从你自己的文件夹导入）保持不变。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「%@」會從你的資料庫中移除。其原始檔案（從你自己的檔案夾匯入）會保持不變。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "[Get a key](https://steamcommunity.com/dev/apikey)  ·  [Steam Web API TOU](https://steamcommunity.com/dev/apiterms)  ·  [About Limited Accounts](https://help.steampowered.com/en/faqs/view/71D3-35C2-AD96-AA3A)" : {
