    "Scratch directories created by the test suites under the container's tmp folder. Debug builds only — no shipping code path writes them. Deleting them affects nothing but disk usage." : {
      "comment" : "Storage tab, debug-only Test Artifacts info popover explaining what the leftover files are.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Scratch directories created by the test suites under the container's tmp folder. Debug builds only — no shipping code path writes them. Deleting them affects nothing but disk usage."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "テストスイートがコンテナの tmp フォルダ内に作成した一時ディレクトリです。デバッグビルド専用で、製品版のコードが書き出すことはありません。削除してもディスク使用量以外に影響はありません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "测试套件在容器 tmp 文件夹下创建的临时目录。仅存在于调试构建，正式版代码不会写入。删除它们除了释放磁盘空间外没有任何影响。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "測試套件在容器 tmp 資料夾下建立的暫存目錄。僅存在於除錯建置，正式版程式碼不會寫入。刪除它們除了釋放磁碟空間外沒有任何影響。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Scripts disabled. Manage in Content Security panel." : {
