          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When off, the app keeps running in the background — reopen this window anytime from the menu bar icon at the top-right of your screen." : {
      "comment" : "Text displayed in a setting row that lets the user toggle whether the app appears in the Dock and the Cmd-Tab switcher.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オフにしてもアプリはバックグラウンドで実行されます — 画面右上のメニューバーアイコンからいつでもこのウインドウを開き直せます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "关闭时，App 会继续在后台运行 — 你随时可以从屏幕右上角的菜单栏图标重新打开此窗口。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "關閉時，App 會繼續在背景執行 — 你隨時可以從螢幕右上角的選單列圖示重新開啟此視窗。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When off, the scene stops following the cursor" : {
      "comment" : "A hint for the user about the effect of disabling",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オフにすると、シーンはカーソルへの追従を停止します"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "关闭时，场景会停止跟随光标"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "關閉時，場景會停止跟隨游標"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, all connected displays render one stretched video. When off, each display plays its own copy independently — multi-display sync is not possible." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, all connected displays render one stretched video. When off, each display plays its own copy independently — multi-display sync is not possible."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オンにすると、接続されているすべてのディスプレイが 1 本の動画を引き伸ばして表示します。オフにすると、各ディスプレイがそれぞれ独立して再生します（マルチディスプレイ同期は不可）。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，所有连接的显示器渲染一段被拉伸的视频；关闭时，每个显示器各自独立播放——多屏无法同步。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟後，所有連接的螢幕渲染一段被拉伸的影片；關閉時，每個螢幕各自獨立播放——多螢幕無法同步。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, clicks and scrolls reach the wallpaper but desktop icons and the Dock become unclickable. Off lets you use Finder normally." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, clicks and scrolls reach the wallpaper but desktop icons and the Dock become unclickable. Off lets you use Finder normally."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オンの場合、クリックとスクロールは壁紙に届きますが、デスクトップアイコンと Dock はクリックできなくなります。オフにすると Finder を通常どおり使用できます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，鼠标点击与滚动作用于壁纸，但桌面图标和 Dock 将无法点击；关闭则可正常使用 Finder。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟時，點按和捲動會傳到桌布，但桌面圖示和 Dock 將無法點按。關閉則可正常使用 Finder。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, the scene captures mouse clicks and the desktop can't be clicked on this display" : {
      "comment" : "A hint for the user about the effect of enabling",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オンにすると、シーンがマウスクリックを取得し、このディスプレイではデスクトップをクリックできません"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启时，场景会捕获鼠标点击，此显示器上的桌面无法点击"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟時，場景會擷取滑鼠點按，此顯示器上的桌面無法點按"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, the wallpaper's WKWebView starts fresh each session — cookies, localStorage, and cache are not persisted" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, the wallpaper's WKWebView starts fresh each session — cookies, localStorage, and cache are not persisted"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オンの場合、壁紙の WKWebView はセッションごとに新規開始します。cookies、localStorage、キャッシュは保持されません"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，壁纸的 WKWebView 每次会话都会重新开始——Cookie、localStorage 和缓存不会保留"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟時，桌布的 WKWebView 每次工作階段都會全新啟動；cookies、localStorage 和快取不會保留"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, the wallpaper's WKWebView starts fresh each session — cookies, localStorage, and cache are not persisted." : {
      "comment" : "Accessibility label for the toggle that lets users choose whether to clear browsing data when the wallpaper exits.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, the wallpaper's WKWebView starts fresh each session — cookies, localStorage, and cache are not persisted."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オンの場合、壁紙の WKWebView はセッションごとに新規開始します。cookies、localStorage、キャッシュは保持されません。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，壁纸的 WKWebView 每次都会从空白开始——Cookie、localStorage 和缓存不会保留。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟時，桌布的 WKWebView 每次工作階段都會全新啟動；cookies、localStorage 和快取不會保留。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, web wallpapers open with WebKit's Web Inspector accessible — right-click in a webview wallpaper to inspect. Recommended only when debugging your own content." : {
      "comment" : "Detailed info popover for the Developer Mode toggle.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, web wallpapers open with WebKit's Web Inspector accessible — right-click in a webview wallpaper to inspect. Recommended only when debugging your own content."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オンにすると、Web 壁紙で WebKit の Web Inspector が使えるようになります — webview 壁紙を右クリックして要素を検証できます。自作コンテンツのデバッグ時のみ推奨します。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，Web 壁纸会启用 WebKit 的 Web Inspector — 在 webview 壁纸上右键即可检查元素。建议仅在调试自有内容时开启。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟後，Web 桌布會啟用 WebKit 的 Web Inspector — 在 webview 桌布上按右鍵即可檢查元素。建議僅在除錯自有內容時開啟。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When open windows cover about 85 percent or more of a display, the wallpaper pauses to free CPU and GPU. It resumes as soon as you reveal the desktop." : {
      "comment" : "Accessibility hint for the \"Pause when windows cover the desktop\" setting.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When open windows cover about 85 percent or more of a display, the wallpaper pauses to free CPU and GPU. It resumes as soon as you reveal the desktop."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開いているウインドウがディスプレイの約 85 パーセント以上を覆うと、CPU と GPU を空けるため壁紙が一時停止します。デスクトップを表示するとすぐ再開します。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "当打开的窗口覆盖某个显示器约百分之 85 或更多区域时，壁纸会暂停以释放 CPU 和 GPU。只要露出桌面就会恢复。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "當開啟的視窗覆蓋某個顯示器約百分之 85 或更多區域時，桌布會暫停以釋放 CPU 和 GPU。只要露出桌面就會恢復。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When windows cover about half the screen, or your Mac is unplugged and wallpapers keep playing, the frame rate drops to about half to save GPU power. Full speed returns once the desktop is visible again. Affects scene (Wallpaper Engine) wallpapers." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When windows cover about half the screen, or your Mac is unplugged and wallpapers keep playing, the frame rate drops to about half to save GPU power. Full speed returns once the desktop is visible again. Affects scene (Wallpaper Engine) wallpapers."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ウインドウが画面の約半分を覆っているとき、または電源に接続されていない状態で壁紙が再生され続けているとき、GPU の電力を節約するためフレームレートが約半分に下がります。デスクトップが再び表示されると通常の速度に戻ります。シーン（Wallpaper Engine）壁紙に適用されます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "当窗口遮挡约一半屏幕，或拔下电源后壁纸仍在播放时，帧率会降到约一半以节省 GPU 功耗。桌面重新可见后恢复全速。适用于场景（Wallpaper Engine）壁纸。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "當視窗遮擋約一半螢幕，或拔下電源後桌布仍在播放時，影格率會降到約一半以節省 GPU 功耗。桌面重新可見後恢復全速。適用於場景（Wallpaper Engine）桌布。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
