            "value" : "你已經有一個 statusLine 命令。它已被排在上面 LiveWallpaper 指令碼之後以繼續生效——把這個設定區塊合併進 ~/.claude/settings.json 即可。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You enter your password and Steam Guard code directly into Valve's official SteamCMD. This app never sees, requests, or stores them." : {
